window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>All climaxes must climax, and this is the climaxest of them all.</p> <p>With the help of a mysterious ally, King Reginald sends a group of elite adventurers to attack the capital city. Surrounded by allies and fortified by his firm faith in those he loves, Thomas will do the unthinkable: join his people in the counter attack. But even if they can defeat the invasion of adventurers, the Goblin King will face an uphill battle.</p> <p>For who sits behind Reginald? And what daunting challenges must King Thomas overcome to finally earn the title of.... <b>ISEKAI EMPEROR?!</b></p>"; 
